snippet.title: Rollie (NES) - trailer
snippet.description:
Video showing off gameplay from Rollie, my NES homebrew platformer, coming  out soon in 2019.

KICKSTARTER: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/optovania/rollie-a-new-game-for-the-classic-nintendo-nes

Game is live on Kickstarter, August 31st - September 30th.

It was developed completely from scratch over the course of 2 years, part time.

GAME SITE: http://rolliegame.com
TWITTER: https://twitter.com/optovania
